726144f.title: Queens: Beach 20th Street - Plainview Avenue
726144f.text:
Beach 20th Street, at the N.W. corner of Plainview Ave., showing
Gerston's Wavecrest Hotel. Eugene L. Armbruster states it was Mrs.
Carroll's house in 1873.
January 1923.
Eugene L. Arabruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
